parameters:
Mikoto...! Is that okay? Hide here until I come to
pick you up!

Hehehe... We can't both hide here. We'll
definitely meet again, so stay put, okay?

It's a promise, right...? You'll definitely come
to get me, right...?
It's a kid! There's a kid here!

What a damn brat, stealing food from the Imperial
Army.

Hmph! It was originally stolen from us in the
first place! Because of that... my mother is...
This damn thief is so noisy!
Gyahahaha! Have you reflected even a little?

Oh, so it's that thief...! Because of this guy, I
got scolded too! I'll give him a piece of my mind.

The Imperial Soldier picks up a fallen liquor
bottle and readies himself.

Gyahahaha! Have you reflected even a little? You
have comrades, right? If you talk, I'll let you
go.
Oh, you've got quite the spirit, don't you?
Well? Are you ready to talk?

(No... I promised mom... I said I would protect
Mikoto...)

Can't be helped, this is the punishment for
opposing the Imperial Army. Regret that you
weren't born into the Empire!
Hahaha! This should curb your appetite a bit.

You guys, judging from the amount of food that's
gone missing, there should still be a culprit
around. Find them.

Hey! You little shit! Don't die just yet. I'm
going to punish you thoroughly.
